    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《重翼再启》  官方群：728784712</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >躲避！射击！飞向更远的星空！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好了吗？驾驶着这架来自远古的战机，在敌人快节奏的进攻中，完成一次又一次的太空旅行吧！灵巧的躲避敌人的攻击，与敌人的弹幕擦肩而过，接着瞄准射击！在布满子弹与陷阱的危险星空中穿行，告诉敌人们，谁才是这条星河的主宰！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/7b7555c350bc9b76f74757b5b45b5b60.poster.avif?t=1758944962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/7b7555c350bc9b76f74757b5b45b5b60.webm?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/7b7555c350bc9b76f74757b5b45b5b60.mp4?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合成！重铸！发现属于你的最强弹药！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在飞行途中，你偶尔能收到敌人掉落的弹药，合成和重铸，搭配它们羁绊获取更多属性加成！发现最符合你的策略和流派的子弹吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/d10fc8889e56f87ab2d61a699c780d1e.poster.avif?t=1758944962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/d10fc8889e56f87ab2d61a699c780d1e.webm?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/d10fc8889e56f87ab2d61a699c780d1e.mp4?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或许你能找到：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >泰瑟枪：在敌人之间形成闪电链！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电磁炮：要聚能一段时间后，释放出超高伤害的穿透能量球！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美杜莎：将生命值低的敌人直接变成一颗陨石！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等超过50种不同的弹药...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级！强化！战胜更强的敌人！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以按照自己的需要，针对性的强化你的战机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/aded7ec3a2643ac7d38df8864c1bb99f.poster.avif?t=1758944962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/aded7ec3a2643ac7d38df8864c1bb99f.webm?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/aded7ec3a2643ac7d38df8864c1bb99f.mp4?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的升级选项能够为你提供：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多的战斗力或生存能力的属性值！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑适合你的战机和弹药的流派！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立刻恢复损失的部分生命值！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让下次升级变得更轻松！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至能让你获得无法从敌人身上掉落的 <strong>传说级 </strong>子弹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和更多能力等你发现。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择合适的<strong>超级技能模块</strong>！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/3b31c1f5b33db1768bcc5343ebdba02f.poster.avif?t=1758944962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/3b31c1f5b33db1768bcc5343ebdba02f.webm?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301280/extras/3b31c1f5b33db1768bcc5343ebdba02f.mp4?t=1758944962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的超级技能模块会给战机提供不同的基础属性和超级技能，包括：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让所有敌人持续减速或受到伤害</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将之前受到的伤害转变为对自身伤害的提升</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体型缩小，且移动的更快</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等十余种模块，等待你的发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与敌人的子弹擦肩而过，就会触发“擦弹”，从而获得更多的充能，在你的充能完成之后，就能够释放超级技能了！</p></li></ul>",
